*Stingtra watched as Quickstrike went fishing and started getting rather
bored she starts to doze off and then she falls out of the tree and lands on
a stick. Then a bunch of fruit falls on top of her covering her up. She
jumps out of the pile of fruit and starts smashing the fruit and punching it
going crazy punching the tree and pants and sits on the ground panting
paying no attention to the sharp stick thats sticking through her stomich*
Stingtra: Having any luck with the fish? *She says to Quickstrike while
panting*

> Quickstrike:
>
>
>
>
> Quickstrike threw his large claw into the water, going for a fish. He
> grumbled as he saw it zip away. He had his tail up high, and targeting. He
> swayed it left and right, watching a handful of fish near-by his boulder.
He
> tail hissed in frustration, having no luck.
>
> He plunged his claw down again, and the fish scattered. He cursed in the
> Predacon language. He was so hungry. He watched after a few moments as the
> fish returned. He leaned his body closer over the edge of the boulder,
> targeting percisely. He plunged his tail down into the water. He felt
> something in between the jaws of his tail. He pulled his tail up and found
> out that he had a catch.
>
> He laughed and snapped his claws in victory. "Ah got one!" he called out.
> "Ah got one!" He turned his body to the side and threw the fish from his
> tail, to the shore. It was already limp.
>
> He looked back down into the waters. He targeted his tail, and tried
again.
> One wasn't going to enough for him.
